data.description: An upgraded NVR Mozart model in the sought after Parkside community! The main level offers 9 ft ceilings, an open floor plan with hardwoods through the entire level (both flights of stairs too), a gourmet kitchen with stainless appliances, granite counters, a large island with barstool seating and an additional eat-in area that leads to a large maintenance free deck off the back overlooking woods.  The upper level offers upstairs laundry, 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths including a master suite with tray ceilings, master bath with dual sinks and a large walk-in shower plus a walk-in closet.  The walkout basement level offers a 1 car garage (driveway parking as well), a powder room and a large rec room with a gas fireplace which leads to the backyard which backs to woods.  All new carpet on the lower and upper levels.  Solar is included and the seller is averaging $155/mo (including the fixed solar lease pmt) compared to similar homes in the neighborhood averaging $225+/mo.  The seller has an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN @ a 3.5% rate for VA buyers! Parkside HOA includes lawn care, a community center, pool, fitness center, playground, and dog park. Easy access to shopping malls, dining, and commuter routes (295, MD-32, and MD-100). Close to Ft. Meade/NSA.
